Total vacancies:453

Name of the Vacancies:

  • Civil Assistant Surgeon Specialist 

Description

The latest central Government Jobs for Post Graduates have been published by Andhra Pradesh Vaidya Vidhana Parishad for Civil Assistant Surgeon Specialist vacancies in Andhra Pradesh. If you are searching for a government job in Andhra Pradesh then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for the vacancies of Civil Assistant Surgeon Specialist, from 14-06-2021, and till 28-06-2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies in Andhra Pradesh and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.

Application fee:

  • The mode of application is Online
  • The application fee for SC & ST Candidates category candidates is only Rs: 1000/-
  • The application fee for OC & BC candidates Candidates category candidates is only Rs: 1500/-

Educational qualification:

  • To apply for a Civil Assistant Surgeon Specialist  in APVVP, your PG Degree/ Diploma/ DNB must be completed from a recognized University

Important dates:

  •  The starting date to apply in these posts is 14-06-2021 
  •  The last date to apply in these posts is 28-06-2021 

Age Limit Criteria:

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 21 to 42 years old. 

APVVP Civil Assistant Surgeon Specialist Pay Scale:

  • According to the information given by the Central Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly

salary is as per norms

How to apply for APVVP Civil Asst. Surgeon Specialist Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process of the Civil Assistant Surgeon Specialist. Fill in your details and submit it or follow all the steps given below.

  •  First, go to the official website of APVVP and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked by APVVP
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.
